ound-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">后台台演示地址</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://shop-manage.hyii2.com/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration: none; outline: none; cursor: pointer;\">http://shop-manage.hyii2.com</a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 宋体;\">帐号：</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">xxx / 123456</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 宋体;\">（<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: red;\">备注：目前xxx</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">账户已开启了大部分权限，如果要使用超级管理员权限请联系“下班闪电去打卡”</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 宋体;\">）</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 24px;\">源码获取</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1.如对源码有浓厚兴趣可自行购买（<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?id=537750350612&qq-pf-to=pcqq.c2c\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"hyii2后台源码淘宝店铺-酱油源码店\" textvalue=\"购买地址\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration: none; outline: none; cursor: pointer;\">购买地址</a>），下单后请联系酱油君、打卡兄 QQ：391430388、443939412</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">特别提醒</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 宋体;\">：只有通过本站购买源码，才能获得以下支持，尊重原创，拒绝盗版！</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">购买后你能得到什么？</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1.一次购买，终生免费，后续更新的所有功能，程序的优化，还有最新的前台模版都可以免费更新。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2.购买源码可用于yii2的学习，并能受到酱油君、打卡兄的亲自辅导。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3.<a href=\"http://www.yii-china.com/doc/detail/3.html\" target=\"_blank\" textvalue=\"对应文档教程\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration: none; outline: none; cursor: pointer;\">对应文档教程</a>&nbsp;(持续更新)<br data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">安装与使用</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1、解压项目文件，将项目文件丢进web服务器中</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2、根据自己需求是否配置域名</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3、将console/data/yii2senior.sql中的数据库文件导入数据库</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4、配置数据库链接</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px;\">方式一：直接修改common/config/main-local.php</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px;\">方式二：修改environments中相应“项目环境”的文件夹下的common/config/main-local.php，然后执行php init来初始化配置</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">效果图：</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"QQ图片20160829141406.png\" src=\"http://up.yii-china.com/image/20160829/1472451191234120.png\" title=\"1472451191234120.png\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://up.yii-china.com/image/20160828/1472365519469335.png\" title=\"1472365519469335.png\" height=\"592\" width=\"1079\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: 1079px; height: 592px;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/><img alt=\"QQ图片20160831173445.png\" src=\"http://up.yii-china.com/image/20160831/1472636036135738.png\" title=\"1472636036135738.png\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">可删除前两个接口的对应代码和配置简化程序。<br data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://up.yii-china.com/image/20160828/1472365519419694.png\" title=\"1472365519419694.png\" height=\"566\" width=\"1078\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: 1078px; height: 566px;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://up.yii-china.com/image/20160828/1472365519553354.png\" title=\"1472365519553354.png\" height=\"582\" width=\"1076\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: 1076px; height: 582px;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"4.jpg.png\" src=\"http://up.yii-china.com/image/20160828/1472366378294389.png\" title=\"1472366378294389.png\" height=\"750\" width=\"1075\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: 1075px; height: 750px;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">PS: 就像文章开篇说的，该商城系统是在yincart2的基础上修改的，因为galaxy是免费版，所以功能不完整且有很多潜在bug和待优化的地方，但本系统已经做进一步完善和功能扩展，大家可以放心使用，使用中遇到任何问题都可以联系我们。有兴趣的朋友也可以去百度上搜索yincart2下载源码自行学习。</p><p><br/></p>', '', 2, 561, 'test', 1, 1516679291, 1516679291);
INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (25, 'Yii2.0 rules验证规则大全 [ 未指定版本 ]', '此小部件实现了文章或项目添加的时候，可以传多张图片，也以对上传成功的图片进行删除（如果配置项 trueDelete 为真， 则服务器上的真实图片也会删除）此小部件不能在上传图片的时', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">required : 必须值验证属性</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">[[&#39;字段名&#39;],required,&#39;requiredValue&#39;=&gt;&#39;必填值&#39;,&#39;message&#39;=&gt;&#39;提示信息&#39;];&nbsp;#说明:CRequiredValidator&nbsp;的别名,&nbsp;确保了特性不为空.</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">email : 邮箱验证</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">[&#39;email&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;email&#39;];&nbsp;#说明:CEmailValidator的别名,确保了特性的值是一个有效的电邮地址.</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">match : 正则验证</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">[[&#39;字段名&#39;],match,&#39;pattern&#39;=&gt;&#39;正则表达式&#39;,&#39;message&#39;=&gt;&#39;提示信息&#39;];&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n[[&#39;字段名&#39;],match,&#39;not&#39;=&gt;ture,&#39;pattern&#39;=&gt;&#39;正则表达式&#39;,&#39;message&#39;=&gt;&#39;提示信息&#39;];&nbsp;/*正则取反*/&nbsp;#说明:CRegularExpressionValidator&nbsp;的别名,&nbsp;确保了特性匹配一个正则表达式.</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">url : 网址</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">[&#39;website&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;url&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;defaultScheme&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;http&#39;];&nbsp;#说明:CUrlValidator&nbsp;的别名,&nbsp;确保了特性是一个有效的路径.</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">captcha : 验证码</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">[&#39;verificationCode&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;captcha&#39;];&nbsp;#说明:CCaptchaValidator&nbsp;的别名,确保了特性的值等于&nbsp;CAPTCHA&nbsp;显示出来的验证码.</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">safe : 安全</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">[&#39;description&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;safe&#39;];</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">compare : 比较</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">[&#39;age&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;compare&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;compareValue&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;30,&nbsp;&#39;operator&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;&gt;=&#39;];&nbsp;#说明:compareValue(比较常量值)&nbsp;-&nbsp;operator(比较操作符)&nbsp;&nbsp;#说明:CCompareValidator&nbsp;的别名,确保了特性的值等于另一个特性或常量.</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">default : 默认值</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">[&#39;age&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;default&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;value&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;null];&nbsp;#说明:CDefaultValueValidator&nbsp;的别名,&nbsp;为特性指派了一个默认值.</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">exist : 存在</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">[&#39;username&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;exist&#39;];&nbsp;#说明:CExistValidator&nbsp;的别名,确保属性值存在于指定的数据表字段中.</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">file : 文件</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">[&#39;primaryImage&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;file&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;extensions&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[&#39;png&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;jpg&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;gif&#39;],&nbsp;&#39;maxSize&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;1024*1024*1024];&nbsp;#说明:CFileValidator&nbsp;的别名,&nbsp;确保了特性包含了一个上传文件的名称.</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">filter : 滤镜</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">[[&#39;username&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;email&#39;],&nbsp;&#39;filter&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;filter&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;trim&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;skipOnArray&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;true];&nbsp;#说明:CFilterValidator&nbsp;的别名,&nbsp;使用一个filter转换属性.</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">in : 范围</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">[&#39;level&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;in&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;range&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[1,&nbsp;2,&nbsp;3]];&nbsp;#说明:CRangeValidator&nbsp;的别名,确保了特性出现在一个预订的值列表里.</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">unique : 唯一性</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">[&#39;username&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;unique&#39;]&nbsp;#说明:CUniqueValidator&nbsp;的别名,确保了特性在数据表字段中是唯一的.</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">integer : 整数</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">[&#39;age&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;integer&#39;];</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">number : 数字</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">[&#39;salary&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;number&#39;];</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">double : 双精度浮点型</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">[&#39;salary&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;double&#39;];</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">date : 日期</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">[[&#39;from&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;to&#39;],&nbsp;&#39;date&#39;];</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">string : 字符串</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">[&#39;username&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;string&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;length&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[4,&nbsp;24]];</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">boolean : 是否为一个布尔值</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">[&#39;字段名&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;boolean&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;trueValue&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;true,&nbsp;&#39;falseValue&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;false,&nbsp;&#39;strict&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;true];&nbsp;#说明:CBooleanValidator&nbsp;的别名</pre><p><br/></p>', '', 3, 561, 'test', 1, 1516679390, 1516679390);
INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (26, 'YiiCMS 一个基于yii2写的后台基础内容管理系统 [基础教程]', 'YiiCMS 一个基于yii2写的后台基础内容管理系统：git地址：https://coding.net/u/GitRong/p/YiiCMS/git只有backend(后台)安装', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">YiiCMS 一个基于yii2写的后台基础内容管理系统：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">git地址：<a href=\"https://coding.net/u/GitRong/p/YiiCMS/git\" _src=\"https://coding.net/u/GitRong/p/YiiCMS/git\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration: none; outline: none; cursor: pointer;\">https://coding.net/u/GitRong/p/YiiCMS/git</a><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">只有backend(后台)</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">安装：</p><ol class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">首先下载下来或者用git克隆下来.</p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">安装composer,并确保全局安装了&#39;composer-asset-plugin&#39;.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p></li><li><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">cd&nbsp;YiiCMS/</pre></li><li><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">composer&nbsp;install</pre></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">在common/config/main-local下配置数据库信息.</p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">新建数据库并导入data/yiidemoad.sql的表结构以及数据.</p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">配置虚拟主机指向backend/web目录并配置好hosts文件域名解析</p></li></ol><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">OK！安装完毕。打开虚拟域名即可访问.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://up.yii-china.com/image/20161010/1476079882371405.png\" title=\"1476079882371405.png\" alt=\"QQ截图20161010140223.png\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;\"/></p><p><br/></p>', '', 2, 561, 'test', 1, 1516679470, 1516679470);
INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (27, 'yii2教程-ActiveForm表单组件', '&nbsp; &nbsp; 向大家推荐一个扩展：yii2-contextmenu， 该扩展为Gird行右击菜单，可以省去操作列。 扩展安装还是比较简单的，英文好的的朋友可以直接去h', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 24px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">简介</strong></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">yii2中最常用的组件activeform,通过对activeform的灵活运用，能有效的提升开发效率，所以这个是不得不说的一个yii2组件，那么下面就来了解一下yii2.0的ActiveForm的具体用法</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 24px;\">用法</span></strong></p><pre class=\"brush:php;toolbar:false\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;?php&nbsp;$form&nbsp;=&nbsp;ActiveForm::begin([&#39;id&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;form-signup&#39;]);&nbsp;?&gt;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//文本框的标题\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;?=&nbsp;$form-&gt;field($model,&nbsp;&#39;test1&#39;)-&gt;label(&#39;文本框的标题&#39;)&nbsp;?&gt;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//文本框下方的提示\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;?=&nbsp;$form-&gt;field($model,&nbsp;&#39;test2&#39;)-&gt;hint(&#39;测试hint&#39;);&nbsp;?&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//input(type)&nbsp;type的类型有&nbsp;text&nbsp;password等\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;?=&nbsp;$form-&gt;field($model,&nbsp;&#39;test3&#39;)-&gt;input(&#39;text&#39;)?&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//简单文本框\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;?=&nbsp;$form-&gt;field($model,&nbsp;&#39;test3&#39;)-&gt;textInput([&#39;maxlength&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;true])?&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//隐藏文本框\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;?=&nbsp;$form-&gt;field($model,&nbsp;&#39;test3&#39;)-&gt;hiddenInput()&nbsp;?&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//密码文本框，应用于登录的密码输入框\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;?=&nbsp;$form-&gt;field($model,&nbsp;&#39;test3&#39;)-&gt;passwordInput()&nbsp;?&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//文本域&nbsp;应用于输入内容较多比如文章简介等&nbsp;rows=&gt;3&nbsp;表示文本域高为3\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;?=&nbsp;$form-&gt;field($model,&nbsp;&#39;test3&#39;)-&gt;textarea([&#39;rows&#39;=&gt;&#39;3&#39;])&nbsp;?&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//文件上传\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;?=&nbsp;$form-&gt;field($model,&nbsp;&#39;test3&#39;)-&gt;fileInput()&nbsp;?&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//勾选框\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;?=&nbsp;$form-&gt;field($model,&nbsp;&#39;test3&#39;)-&gt;radio()&nbsp;?&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//多选框\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;?=&nbsp;$form-&gt;field($model,&nbsp;&#39;test3&#39;)-&gt;checkbox()&nbsp;?&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//listbox&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;?=&nbsp;$form-&gt;field($model,&nbsp;&#39;test3&#39;)-&gt;listBox([&#39;0&#39;=&gt;&#39;box1&#39;,&#39;1&#39;=&gt;&#39;box2&#39;])&nbsp;?&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//多谢框列表，常用\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;?=&nbsp;$form-&gt;field($model,&nbsp;&#39;test3&#39;)-&gt;checkboxList([&#39;0&#39;=&gt;&#39;box1&#39;,&#39;1&#39;=&gt;&#39;box2&#39;])&nbsp;?&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//单选框列表，常用\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;?=&nbsp;$form-&gt;field($model,&nbsp;&#39;test3&#39;)-&gt;radioList([&#39;0&#39;=&gt;&#39;radio1&#39;,&#39;1&#39;=&gt;&#39;radio2&#39;])?&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//下拉框列表\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;?=&nbsp;$form-&gt;field($model,&nbsp;&#39;test3&#39;)-&gt;dropDownList(\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[&#39;1&#39;=&gt;&#39;下拉选项1&#39;,&#39;2&#39;=&gt;&#39;下拉选项2&#39;],\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[&#39;prompt&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;请选择&#39;]\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;)&nbsp;?&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//插件组件应用，比如yii2编辑器插件，图片上传插件\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;?=&nbsp;$form-&gt;field($model,&#39;test3&#39;)-&gt;widget(yii\\captcha\\Captcha::className())?&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;div&nbsp;class=&quot;form-group&quot;&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;?=&nbsp;Html::submitButton(&#39;按钮&#39;,&nbsp;[&#39;class&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;btn&nbsp;btn-primary&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;name&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;signup-button&#39;])&nbsp;?&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;?php&nbsp;ActiveForm::end();&nbsp;?&gt;</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">上面基本涵盖了activeform的所有文本框的例子，但是如果我们需要对表单的结构做自定义的调整，以适用每个不同项目的需求，那是不是就没法用activeform了？请看下面自定义表单结构</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 24px;\">自定义表单结构</span></strong></p><pre class=\"brush:php;toolbar:false\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">use&nbsp;yii\\bootstrap\\ActiveForm;\r\n\r\n$form&nbsp;=&nbsp;ActiveForm::begin([&#39;layout&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;horizontal&#39;]);\r\n\r\n//&nbsp;隐藏form的标签&nbsp;\r\necho&nbsp;$form-&gt;field($model,&nbsp;&#39;demo&#39;,&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;inputOptions&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;placeholder&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;$model-&gt;getAttributeLabel(&#39;demo&#39;),\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],\r\n&nbsp;])-&gt;label(false);\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;//&nbsp;内联&nbsp;radio&nbsp;list\r\n&nbsp;echo&nbsp;$form-&gt;field($model,&nbsp;&#39;demo&#39;)-&gt;inline()-&gt;radioList($items);\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;//水平模式控制文本框的大小\r\n&nbsp;echo&nbsp;$form-&gt;field($model,&nbsp;&#39;demo&#39;,&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;horizontalCssClasses&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;wrapper&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;col-sm-2&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;]\r\n&nbsp;]);\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;//&nbsp;除了&#39;default（默认）&#39;&nbsp;布局&nbsp;你还可以用&nbsp;&#39;template&#39;&nbsp;制定特定的布局:\r\n&nbsp;echo&nbsp;$form-&gt;field($model,&nbsp;&#39;demo&#39;,&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;template&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;{label}&nbsp;&lt;div&nbsp;class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;&lt;div&nbsp;class=&quot;col-sm-4&quot;&gt;{input}{error}{hint}&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#39;\r\n&nbsp;]);\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;//&nbsp;自定义输入框的结构\r\n&nbsp;echo&nbsp;$form-&gt;field($model,&nbsp;&#39;demo&#39;,&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;inputTemplate&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;&lt;div&nbsp;class=&quot;input-group&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;class=&quot;input-group-addon&quot;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;{input}&lt;/div&gt;&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;]);\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;ActiveForm::end();</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 24px;\">详细参数</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">[[\\yii\\widgets\\ActiveField]]. 加强版的Bootstrap 3<br data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1.这个类添加了一些有用的功能到 [[\\yii\\widgets\\ActiveField|ActiveField]] 在不同的形式布局中提供各种bootstrap3的表单域:</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">-&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">[[inputTemplate]]</span>&nbsp;是一个用来呈现复杂输入的可选模板，例如输入组<br data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">-&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">[[horizontalCssClasses]]</span>&nbsp;以横向形式定义了css网络格以增加标签，包装和错误提示</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">-&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">[[inline]]/[[inline()]]</span>&nbsp;被用于提供内联的[[checkboxList()]] 和[[radioList()]]</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">-&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">[[enableError]]</span>&nbsp;被设置为‘false’以禁用错误</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">-&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">[[enableLabel]]</span>&nbsp;被设置为`false` 以禁用标签</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">-&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">[[label()]]</span>&nbsp;和boolean值一起使用，来启用和禁用标签</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2.也有一些新的占位符，你可以用在 [[template]] 结构中：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">- `<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(146, 208, 80);\">{beginLabel}</span>`: 开始标签</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">- `<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(146, 208, 80);\">{labelTitle}</span>`: 标签的标题，和 `{beginLabel}`/`{endLabel}`一起使用</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">- `<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(146, 208, 80);\">{endLabel}</span>`: 结束标签</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">- `<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(146, 208, 80);\">{beginWrapper}</span>`: 开始包装标签</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">- `<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(146, 208, 80);\">{endWrapper}</span>`: 关闭包装标签</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3.包装标签仅用于某些布局和表单元素.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">请注意，某些元素使用了 [[template]]的轻微不同的默认值和其他选项.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">你可以重写这些预定义模板复选框, radio buttons, checkboxLists和 radioLists 在 [[\\yii\\widgets\\ActiveForm::fieldConfig|fieldConfig]] 的</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">[[\\yii\\widgets\\ActiveForm]]:</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">-&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">[[checkboxTemplate]]</span>&nbsp;在默认布局复选框模板</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">-&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">[[radioTemplate]]</span>&nbsp;默认布局中的radio button模板&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">-&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">[[horizontalCheckboxTemplate]]</span>&nbsp;水平布局的 checkboxes模块</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">-&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">[[horizontalRadioTemplate]]</span>&nbsp;水平布局的 radio buttons 模块</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">-&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">[[inlineCheckboxListTemplate]]</span>&nbsp;内联的 checkboxLists模块</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">-&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">[[inlineRadioListTemplate]]</span>&nbsp;内联的 radioLists模块</p>', '', 3, 561, 'test', 1, 1516679755, 1516679755);
INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (28, 'Yii2 应用 swoole 的两种思路', '我们理解和使用yii2和swoole的过程中，总会有一些疑惑、想法。现在记录下来，整理笔记、知识，并将其中的价值传播给他人，分享知识。本文将重点介绍: (*注: 系统环境：php ', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我们理解和使用yii2和swoole的过程中，总会有一些疑惑、想法。现在记录下来，整理笔记、知识，并将其中的价值传播给他人，分享知识。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">本文将重点介绍: (*注: 系统环境：php 5.6 + swoole 1.9)</p><blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 14px; border-left: 5px solid rgb(229, 229, 229); background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 20px;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>1.yii2控制台程序如何应用swoole（tcp服务器）</p></li><li><p>2.yii2restful如何应用swoole（http服务器）</p></li></ul></blockquote><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1.yii2 控制台程序应用swoole</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">WHY：利用yii2控制台程序，启动一个swoole tcp服务。（将yii2作为容器，其内运行sw服务）</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">HOW：1.1 在控制器方法中，参照swoole文档回调函数配置，启动一个最简单tcp服务，然后运行./yii swt-tcp/run 即可。</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">&lt;?phpnamespace&nbsp;app\\commands;use&nbsp;yii\\console\\Controller;class&nbsp;SwTcpController&nbsp;extends&nbsp;Controller{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;sw&nbsp;tcp&nbsp;服务\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;private&nbsp;$_tcp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;控制台应用方法\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;actionRun()\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_tcp&nbsp;=&nbsp;new&nbsp;\\swoole_server(&#39;0.0.0.0&#39;,&nbsp;9503);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_tcp-&gt;on(&#39;connect&#39;,&nbsp;[$this,&nbsp;&#39;onConnect&#39;]);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_tcp-&gt;on(&#39;receive&#39;,&nbsp;[$this,&nbsp;&#39;onReceive&#39;]);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_tcp-&gt;on(&#39;close&#39;,&nbsp;[$this,&nbsp;&#39;onClose&#39;]);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_tcp-&gt;start();\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;sw&nbsp;connect&nbsp;回调函数\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;onConnect($server,&nbsp;$fd)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;&quot;connection&nbsp;open:&nbsp;{$fd}\\n&quot;;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;sw&nbsp;receive&nbsp;回调函数\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;onReceive($server,&nbsp;$fd,&nbsp;$reactor_id,&nbsp;$data)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;向客户端发送数据\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$server-&gt;send($fd,&nbsp;&quot;Swoole:&nbsp;{$data}&quot;);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;关闭客户端\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$server-&gt;close($fd);\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;sw&nbsp;close&nbsp;回调函数\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;onClose($server,&nbsp;$fd)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;&quot;connection&nbsp;close:&nbsp;{$fd}\\n&quot;;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n}</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1.2 手写一个tcp客户端测试脚本 tcp_client.php，这里采用swoole官网tcp客户端栗子。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">然后 php tcp_client.php 运行，就可以愉快的进行数据交互了。</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">&lt;?php//&nbsp;tcp&nbsp;client$client&nbsp;=&nbsp;new&nbsp;\\swoole_client(SWOOLE_SOCK_TCP,&nbsp;SWOOLE_SOCK_ASYNC);\r\n$client-&gt;on(&quot;connect&quot;,&nbsp;function&nbsp;($cli)&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$cli-&gt;send(&quot;hello&nbsp;world\\n&quot;);\r\n});\r\n$client-&gt;on(&quot;receive&quot;,&nbsp;function&nbsp;($cli,&nbsp;$data)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;&quot;received:&nbsp;{$data}\\n&quot;;\r\n});\r\n$client-&gt;on(&quot;error&quot;,&nbsp;function&nbsp;($cli)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;&quot;connect&nbsp;failed\\n&quot;;\r\n});\r\n$client-&gt;on(&quot;close&quot;,&nbsp;function&nbsp;($cli)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;&quot;connection&nbsp;close\\n&quot;;\r\n});\r\n$client-&gt;connect(&quot;127.0.0.1&quot;,&nbsp;9503,&nbsp;0.5);</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">WHAT：至此一个tcp服务器就完成了，然后我们就可以应用yii2强大的功能组件快乐的编写代码了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">服务端通过解析json中的cmd（命令字）进行分发处理并响应。</p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2.yii2 restful应用swoole</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">WHY：手写一个swoole http 服务脚本，在其onRequest回调函数中，模拟fpm环境，运行yii2应用。（将sw作为容器，其内运行yii2服务）</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">HOW：2.1 这里我们只需要将index.php稍微改造一下即可，把实例化应用主体放到sw workstart进程中，并模拟请求环境。</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">&lt;?phpclass&nbsp;swHttp&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;private&nbsp;$_http;&nbsp;&nbsp;	//&nbsp;程序启动入口\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;run($conf)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_http&nbsp;=&nbsp;new&nbsp;\\swoole_http_server(&#39;0.0.0.0&#39;,&nbsp;9501);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_http-&gt;on(&#39;start&#39;,&nbsp;[$this,&#39;onStart&#39;]);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_http-&gt;on(&#39;WorkerStart&#39;,&nbsp;[$this,&#39;onWorkerStart&#39;]);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_http-&gt;on(&#39;request&#39;,&nbsp;[$this,&#39;onRequest&#39;]);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_http-&gt;set($conf);&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_http-&gt;start();\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;onStart($server)&nbsp;{}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;onWorkerStart($server,&nbsp;$worker_id)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;加载配置文件，启动一个web应用\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$config&nbsp;=&nbsp;include(__DIR__&nbsp;.&nbsp;&#39;/../config/web.php&#39;);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;new&nbsp;\\app\\web\\Application($config);\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;onRequest($request,&nbsp;$response)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;由于sw&nbsp;接管所有环境变量，这里我们设置模拟yii2应用请求所需要的环境即可\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;setYii2Env($request,&nbsp;$response);\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Yii::$app-&gt;run();\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;setYii2Env($request,&nbsp;$response)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;在yii2&nbsp;request组件中保存sw&nbsp;request对象，参考重写后的request组件\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Yii::$app-&gt;request-&gt;setSwRequest($request);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;在yii2&nbsp;response组件中保存sw&nbsp;response对象，参考重写后的request组件\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Yii::$app-&gt;response-&gt;setSwResponse($response);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;设置yii2请求环境，参考重写后的request组件\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Yii::$app-&gt;request-&gt;setRequestEnv();&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;	//&nbsp;由于是常驻服务，需要清除上一次响应信息\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Yii::$app-&gt;response-&gt;clear();\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n}//-----------------&nbsp;yii2&nbsp;web&nbsp;application--------defined(&#39;YII_DEBUG&#39;)&nbsp;or&nbsp;define(&#39;YII_DEBUG&#39;,&nbsp;true);\r\ndefined(&#39;YII_ENV&#39;)&nbsp;or&nbsp;define(&#39;YII_ENV&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;dev&#39;);require(__DIR__&nbsp;.&nbsp;&#39;/../vendor/autoload.php&#39;);require(__DIR__&nbsp;.&nbsp;&#39;/../vendor/yiisoft/yii2/Yii.php&#39;);require(__DIR__&nbsp;.&nbsp;&#39;/../web/Application.php&#39;);//-----------------&nbsp;sw&nbsp;config&nbsp;-------------------$swConf&nbsp;=&nbsp;[&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;pid_file&#39;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;__DIR__&nbsp;.&nbsp;&#39;/server.pid&#39;,&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;worker_num&#39;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;4,&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;max_request&#39;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;1000,&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;daemonize&#39;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;0,\r\n];\r\n(new&nbsp;swHttp())-&gt;run($swConf);</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2.2 yii2 request、response组件重写</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Q：为什么要重写yii2的组件？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">A：其一需要扩展组件的方法，其二需要组件方法需sw兼容。随手一个栗子respone组件来说，其底层最终通过echo 输出数据到客户端，而在swoole中，echo 是输出到控制台，需要使用其$respone-&gt;end()方法才可以输出数据到客户端。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Q：如何重写？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">A：通过配置组件类即可，这里以响应组件为栗子，参考下列代码：</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">&#39;components&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;...&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;response&#39;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;	//&nbsp;重写后的response组件类\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;class&#39;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;\\app\\components\\Response::class,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;format&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;\\yii\\web\\Response::FORMAT_JSON,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">具体的重写后的response组件代码：</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">&lt;?phpnamespace&nbsp;app\\components;//&nbsp;继承底层&nbsp;web&nbsp;responseclass&nbsp;Response&nbsp;extends&nbsp;\\yii\\web\\Response{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;private&nbsp;$_swResponse;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;setSwResponse($response)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swResponse&nbsp;=&nbsp;$response;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;getSwResponse()\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swResponse;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;sendHeaders()\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$headers&nbsp;=&nbsp;$this-&gt;getHeaders();&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;($headers-&gt;count&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;0)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;foreach&nbsp;($headers&nbsp;as&nbsp;$name&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;$values)&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$name&nbsp;=&nbsp;str_replace(&#39;&nbsp;&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;-&#39;,&nbsp;ucwords(str_replace(&#39;-&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;&nbsp;&#39;,&nbsp;$name)));&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;foreach&nbsp;($values&nbsp;as&nbsp;$value)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swResponse-&gt;header($name,&nbsp;$value);\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swResponse-&gt;status($this-&gt;getStatusCode());\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;需要重写的方法，这里我们只需要更改echo&nbsp;为&nbsp;swoole的response输出即可\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;sendContent()\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;($this-&gt;stream&nbsp;===&nbsp;null)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;($this-&gt;content)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;	//&nbsp;输出数据到客户端，这里需要使用sw&nbsp;response对象来输出\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//echo&nbsp;$this-&gt;content;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swResponse-&gt;end($this-&gt;content);\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;else&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swResponse-&gt;end();\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$chunkSize&nbsp;=&nbsp;2&nbsp;*&nbsp;1024&nbsp;*&nbsp;1024;&nbsp;//&nbsp;2MB&nbsp;per&nbsp;chunk&nbsp;swoole&nbsp;limit\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;(is_array($this-&gt;stream))&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;list&nbsp;($handle,&nbsp;$begin,&nbsp;$end)&nbsp;=&nbsp;$this-&gt;stream;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;fseek($handle,&nbsp;$begin);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;while&nbsp;(!feof($handle)&nbsp;&amp;&amp;&nbsp;($pos&nbsp;=&nbsp;ftell($handle))&nbsp;&lt;=&nbsp;$end)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;($pos&nbsp;+&nbsp;$chunkSize&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;$end)&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$chunkSize&nbsp;=&nbsp;$end&nbsp;-&nbsp;$pos&nbsp;+&nbsp;1;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;同上\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swResponse-&gt;write(fread($handle,&nbsp;$chunkSize));\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;flush();&nbsp;//&nbsp;Free&nbsp;up&nbsp;memory.&nbsp;Otherwise&nbsp;large&nbsp;files&nbsp;will&nbsp;trigger&nbsp;PHP&#39;s&nbsp;memory&nbsp;limit.\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;fclose($handle);\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;else&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;while&nbsp;(!feof($this-&gt;stream))&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swResponse-&gt;write(fread($this-&gt;stream,&nbsp;$chunkSize));\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;flush();\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;fclose($this-&gt;stream);\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;同上\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swResponse-&gt;end();\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n}</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">然后还有我们常用的request组件:</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">注：如果我们需要通过yii2 request组件获取get参数信息，直接通过getQueryParams方法是取不到参数信息的，因为参数都在sw 的request对象中，所以这里我们有我们有两种方式可以实现参数获取：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">	1：将其getQueryParams方法进行重写（栗子在下面）。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">	2：不进行重写，设置环境变量（将sw接收到的get数据放置 $_GET中，栗子在下面）</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">&lt;?phpnamespace&nbsp;app\\components;class&nbsp;Request&nbsp;extends&nbsp;\\yii\\web\\Request&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;private&nbsp;$_swRequest;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;setSwRequest($request)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swRequest&nbsp;=&nbsp;$request;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;getSwRequest()&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swRequest;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;/***\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;重写的栗子\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;getQueryParams()\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;($this-&gt;_queryParams&nbsp;===&nbsp;null)&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//return&nbsp;$_GET;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;重写其参数获取方式\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;	return&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swRequest-&gt;get;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;$this-&gt;_queryParams;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;***/\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;模拟fpm请求环境，将sw接收的数据赋值给yii2请求变量中（如果还需要其他信息，自行添加即可）\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;setRequestEnv()&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;header&nbsp;信息设置\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;getHeaders()-&gt;removeAll();&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;foreach&nbsp;($this-&gt;_swRequest-&gt;header&nbsp;as&nbsp;$name&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;$value)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;getHeaders()-&gt;add($name,&nbsp;$value);\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;参数信息设置\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$_GET&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&nbsp;isset($this-&gt;_swRequest-&gt;get)&nbsp;?&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swRequest-&gt;get&nbsp;:&nbsp;[];\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$_POST&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&nbsp;isset($this-&gt;_swRequest-&gt;post)&nbsp;?&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swRequest-&gt;post&nbsp;:&nbsp;[];\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$_SERVER[&#39;REQUEST_METHOD&#39;]&nbsp;=&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swRequest-&gt;server[&#39;request_method&#39;];&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;setBodyParams(null);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;setRawBody($this-&gt;_swRequest-&gt;rawContent());&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;路由设置\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;setPathInfo($this-&gt;_swRequest-&gt;server[&#39;path_info&#39;]);\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n}</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">最后提一点Yii2中的其他组件：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">errorHandler组件：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">	由于 sw 程序中禁止使用exit/die 方法，所以 ErrorHandler 需要改写其中的异常退出方法。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Log 组件：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">	sw提供异步写文件，这里是不是可以改进一下，写一个自己的异步写日志的组件，提高性能。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">...</p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3.结尾</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">tcp服务不在赘述，http服务相对来说更复杂写，但是明白其中解析过程（onRequest事件 -&gt; 设置yii2请求环境-&gt; 运行yii2应用）和运行原理，以及相关组件兼容写法，也就不那么难了。（写了这么多如果还是不明白，扫一扫下面的微信二维码，你就会和我一样，立马解锁更多思路）</p><p>附：<a href=\"https://github.com/degree66/swoole-yii2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(35, 82, 124); outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">https://github.com/degree66/swoole-yii2</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&quot;github原装代码&quot;</span></p>', '', 1, 563, '白衣少侠', 1, 1523435376, 1523435376);
INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (29, '测试插件', '测试中', '<p>测试中</p>', '/image/upload/20180417/1523895238103117.jpg', 2, 563, '白衣少侠', 1, 1523810384, 1523810384);
INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (30, 'yii2 bootstrap组件-警告框（Alert）', '简介yii2 Alert组件是一个基于bootstrap的扩展，那么我们要如何使用yii2 Alert框呢？请看下面的实例实例&lt;?php\r\nuseyii\\bootstrap\\', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 24px;\">简介</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">yii2 Alert组件是一个基于bootstrap的扩展，那么我们要如何使用yii2 Alert框呢？请看下面的实例</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 24px;\">实例</span></strong></p><pre class=\"brush:php;toolbar:false\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">&lt;?php\r\nuse&nbsp;yii\\bootstrap\\Alert;\r\necho&nbsp;Alert::widget([\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;options&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;class&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;alert-info&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;],\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;body&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;保存失败！&#39;,\r\n]);</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">以上实例可以看到，输出一个警告框非常简单，配置bootstrap样式以及输出内容即可迅速生成一个页面警告框。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当然yii2 Alert还有另外的写法</p><pre class=\"brush:php;toolbar:false\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">Alert::begin([\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;options&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;class&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;alert-warning&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;],\r\n]);\r\necho&nbsp;&#39;保存失败！&#39;;\r\nAlert::end();</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 24px;\">演示</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://up.yii-china.com/image/20160725/1469434287188295.png\" title=\"1469434287188295.png\" alt=\"blob.png\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;\"/></p>', '', 5, 563, '白衣少侠', 1, 1524222013, 1524222013);
INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (31, 'Yii2 应用 swoole 的两种思路', '我们理解和使用yii2和swoole的过程中，总会有一些疑惑、想法。现在记录下来，整理笔记、知识，并将其中的价值传播给他人，分享知识。本文将重点介绍: (*注: 系统环境：php ', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我们理解和使用yii2和swoole的过程中，总会有一些疑惑、想法。现在记录下来，整理笔记、知识，并将其中的价值传播给他人，分享知识。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">本文将重点介绍: (*注: 系统环境：php 5.6 + swoole 1.9)</p><blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 14px; border-left: 5px solid rgb(229, 229, 229); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;\"><ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px;\"><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">1.yii2控制台程序如何应用swoole（tcp服务器）</p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">2.yii2restful如何应用swoole（http服务器）</p></li></ul></blockquote><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1.yii2 控制台程序应用swoole</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">WHY：利用yii2控制台程序，启动一个swoole tcp服务。（将yii2作为容器，其内运行sw服务）</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">HOW：1.1 在控制器方法中，参照swoole文档回调函数配置，启动一个最简单tcp服务，然后运行./yii swt-tcp/run 即可。</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">&lt;?phpnamespace&nbsp;app\\commands;use&nbsp;yii\\console\\Controller;class&nbsp;SwTcpController&nbsp;extends&nbsp;Controller{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;sw&nbsp;tcp&nbsp;服务\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;private&nbsp;$_tcp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;控制台应用方法\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;actionRun()\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_tcp&nbsp;=&nbsp;new&nbsp;\\swoole_server(&#39;0.0.0.0&#39;,&nbsp;9503);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_tcp-&gt;on(&#39;connect&#39;,&nbsp;[$this,&nbsp;&#39;onConnect&#39;]);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_tcp-&gt;on(&#39;receive&#39;,&nbsp;[$this,&nbsp;&#39;onReceive&#39;]);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_tcp-&gt;on(&#39;close&#39;,&nbsp;[$this,&nbsp;&#39;onClose&#39;]);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_tcp-&gt;start();\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;sw&nbsp;connect&nbsp;回调函数\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;onConnect($server,&nbsp;$fd)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;&quot;connection&nbsp;open:&nbsp;{$fd}\\n&quot;;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;sw&nbsp;receive&nbsp;回调函数\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;onReceive($server,&nbsp;$fd,&nbsp;$reactor_id,&nbsp;$data)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;向客户端发送数据\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$server-&gt;send($fd,&nbsp;&quot;Swoole:&nbsp;{$data}&quot;);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;关闭客户端\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$server-&gt;close($fd);\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;sw&nbsp;close&nbsp;回调函数\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;onClose($server,&nbsp;$fd)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;&quot;connection&nbsp;close:&nbsp;{$fd}\\n&quot;;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n}</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1.2 手写一个tcp客户端测试脚本 tcp_client.php，这里采用swoole官网tcp客户端栗子。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">然后 php tcp_client.php 运行，就可以愉快的进行数据交互了。</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">&lt;?php//&nbsp;tcp&nbsp;client$client&nbsp;=&nbsp;new&nbsp;\\swoole_client(SWOOLE_SOCK_TCP,&nbsp;SWOOLE_SOCK_ASYNC);\r\n$client-&gt;on(&quot;connect&quot;,&nbsp;function&nbsp;($cli)&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$cli-&gt;send(&quot;hello&nbsp;world\\n&quot;);\r\n});\r\n$client-&gt;on(&quot;receive&quot;,&nbsp;function&nbsp;($cli,&nbsp;$data)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;&quot;received:&nbsp;{$data}\\n&quot;;\r\n});\r\n$client-&gt;on(&quot;error&quot;,&nbsp;function&nbsp;($cli)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;&quot;connect&nbsp;failed\\n&quot;;\r\n});\r\n$client-&gt;on(&quot;close&quot;,&nbsp;function&nbsp;($cli)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;&quot;connection&nbsp;close\\n&quot;;\r\n});\r\n$client-&gt;connect(&quot;127.0.0.1&quot;,&nbsp;9503,&nbsp;0.5);</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">WHAT：至此一个tcp服务器就完成了，然后我们就可以应用yii2强大的功能组件快乐的编写代码了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">服务端通过解析json中的cmd（命令字）进行分发处理并响应。</p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2.yii2 restful应用swoole</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">WHY：手写一个swoole http 服务脚本，在其onRequest回调函数中，模拟fpm环境，运行yii2应用。（将sw作为容器，其内运行yii2服务）</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">HOW：2.1 这里我们只需要将index.php稍微改造一下即可，把实例化应用主体放到sw workstart进程中，并模拟请求环境。</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">&lt;?phpclass&nbsp;swHttp&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;private&nbsp;$_http;&nbsp;&nbsp;	//&nbsp;程序启动入口\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;run($conf)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_http&nbsp;=&nbsp;new&nbsp;\\swoole_http_server(&#39;0.0.0.0&#39;,&nbsp;9501);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_http-&gt;on(&#39;start&#39;,&nbsp;[$this,&#39;onStart&#39;]);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_http-&gt;on(&#39;WorkerStart&#39;,&nbsp;[$this,&#39;onWorkerStart&#39;]);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_http-&gt;on(&#39;request&#39;,&nbsp;[$this,&#39;onRequest&#39;]);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_http-&gt;set($conf);&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_http-&gt;start();\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;onStart($server)&nbsp;{}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;onWorkerStart($server,&nbsp;$worker_id)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;加载配置文件，启动一个web应用\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$config&nbsp;=&nbsp;include(__DIR__&nbsp;.&nbsp;&#39;/../config/web.php&#39;);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;new&nbsp;\\app\\web\\Application($config);\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;onRequest($request,&nbsp;$response)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;由于sw&nbsp;接管所有环境变量，这里我们设置模拟yii2应用请求所需要的环境即可\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;setYii2Env($request,&nbsp;$response);\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Yii::$app-&gt;run();\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;setYii2Env($request,&nbsp;$response)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;在yii2&nbsp;request组件中保存sw&nbsp;request对象，参考重写后的request组件\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Yii::$app-&gt;request-&gt;setSwRequest($request);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;在yii2&nbsp;response组件中保存sw&nbsp;response对象，参考重写后的request组件\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Yii::$app-&gt;response-&gt;setSwResponse($response);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;设置yii2请求环境，参考重写后的request组件\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Yii::$app-&gt;request-&gt;setRequestEnv();&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;	//&nbsp;由于是常驻服务，需要清除上一次响应信息\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Yii::$app-&gt;response-&gt;clear();\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n}//-----------------&nbsp;yii2&nbsp;web&nbsp;application--------defined(&#39;YII_DEBUG&#39;)&nbsp;or&nbsp;define(&#39;YII_DEBUG&#39;,&nbsp;true);\r\ndefined(&#39;YII_ENV&#39;)&nbsp;or&nbsp;define(&#39;YII_ENV&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;dev&#39;);require(__DIR__&nbsp;.&nbsp;&#39;/../vendor/autoload.php&#39;);require(__DIR__&nbsp;.&nbsp;&#39;/../vendor/yiisoft/yii2/Yii.php&#39;);require(__DIR__&nbsp;.&nbsp;&#39;/../web/Application.php&#39;);//-----------------&nbsp;sw&nbsp;config&nbsp;-------------------$swConf&nbsp;=&nbsp;[&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;pid_file&#39;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;__DIR__&nbsp;.&nbsp;&#39;/server.pid&#39;,&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;worker_num&#39;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;4,&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;max_request&#39;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;1000,&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;daemonize&#39;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;0,\r\n];\r\n(new&nbsp;swHttp())-&gt;run($swConf);</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2.2 yii2 request、response组件重写</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Q：为什么要重写yii2的组件？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">A：其一需要扩展组件的方法，其二需要组件方法需sw兼容。随手一个栗子respone组件来说，其底层最终通过echo 输出数据到客户端，而在swoole中，echo 是输出到控制台，需要使用其$respone-&gt;end()方法才可以输出数据到客户端。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Q：如何重写？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">A：通过配置组件类即可，这里以响应组件为栗子，参考下列代码：</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">&#39;components&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;...&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;response&#39;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;	//&nbsp;重写后的response组件类\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;class&#39;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;\\app\\components\\Response::class,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;format&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;\\yii\\web\\Response::FORMAT_JSON,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">具体的重写后的response组件代码：</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">&lt;?phpnamespace&nbsp;app\\components;//&nbsp;继承底层&nbsp;web&nbsp;responseclass&nbsp;Response&nbsp;extends&nbsp;\\yii\\web\\Response{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;private&nbsp;$_swResponse;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;setSwResponse($response)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swResponse&nbsp;=&nbsp;$response;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;getSwResponse()\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swResponse;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;sendHeaders()\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$headers&nbsp;=&nbsp;$this-&gt;getHeaders();&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;($headers-&gt;count&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;0)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;foreach&nbsp;($headers&nbsp;as&nbsp;$name&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;$values)&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$name&nbsp;=&nbsp;str_replace(&#39;&nbsp;&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;-&#39;,&nbsp;ucwords(str_replace(&#39;-&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;&nbsp;&#39;,&nbsp;$name)));&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;foreach&nbsp;($values&nbsp;as&nbsp;$value)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swResponse-&gt;header($name,&nbsp;$value);\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swResponse-&gt;status($this-&gt;getStatusCode());\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;需要重写的方法，这里我们只需要更改echo&nbsp;为&nbsp;swoole的response输出即可\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;sendContent()\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;($this-&gt;stream&nbsp;===&nbsp;null)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;($this-&gt;content)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;	//&nbsp;输出数据到客户端，这里需要使用sw&nbsp;response对象来输出\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//echo&nbsp;$this-&gt;content;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swResponse-&gt;end($this-&gt;content);\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;else&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swResponse-&gt;end();\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$chunkSize&nbsp;=&nbsp;2&nbsp;*&nbsp;1024&nbsp;*&nbsp;1024;&nbsp;//&nbsp;2MB&nbsp;per&nbsp;chunk&nbsp;swoole&nbsp;limit\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;(is_array($this-&gt;stream))&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;list&nbsp;($handle,&nbsp;$begin,&nbsp;$end)&nbsp;=&nbsp;$this-&gt;stream;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;fseek($handle,&nbsp;$begin);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;while&nbsp;(!feof($handle)&nbsp;&amp;&amp;&nbsp;($pos&nbsp;=&nbsp;ftell($handle))&nbsp;&lt;=&nbsp;$end)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;($pos&nbsp;+&nbsp;$chunkSize&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;$end)&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$chunkSize&nbsp;=&nbsp;$end&nbsp;-&nbsp;$pos&nbsp;+&nbsp;1;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;同上\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swResponse-&gt;write(fread($handle,&nbsp;$chunkSize));\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;flush();&nbsp;//&nbsp;Free&nbsp;up&nbsp;memory.&nbsp;Otherwise&nbsp;large&nbsp;files&nbsp;will&nbsp;trigger&nbsp;PHP&#39;s&nbsp;memory&nbsp;limit.\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;fclose($handle);\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;else&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;while&nbsp;(!feof($this-&gt;stream))&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swResponse-&gt;write(fread($this-&gt;stream,&nbsp;$chunkSize));\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;flush();\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;fclose($this-&gt;stream);\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;同上\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swResponse-&gt;end();\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n}</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">然后还有我们常用的request组件:</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">注：如果我们需要通过yii2 request组件获取get参数信息，直接通过getQueryParams方法是取不到参数信息的，因为参数都在sw 的request对象中，所以这里我们有我们有两种方式可以实现参数获取：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1：将其getQueryParams方法进行重写（栗子在下面）。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2：不进行重写，设置环境变量（将sw接收到的get数据放置 $_GET中，栗子在下面）</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">&lt;?phpnamespace&nbsp;app\\components;class&nbsp;Request&nbsp;extends&nbsp;\\yii\\web\\Request&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;private&nbsp;$_swRequest;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;setSwRequest($request)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swRequest&nbsp;=&nbsp;$request;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;getSwRequest()&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swRequest;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;/***\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;重写的栗子\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;getQueryParams()\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;($this-&gt;_queryParams&nbsp;===&nbsp;null)&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//return&nbsp;$_GET;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;重写其参数获取方式\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;	return&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swRequest-&gt;get;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;$this-&gt;_queryParams;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;***/\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;模拟fpm请求环境，将sw接收的数据赋值给yii2请求变量中（如果还需要其他信息，自行添加即可）\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;setRequestEnv()&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;header&nbsp;信息设置\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;getHeaders()-&gt;removeAll();&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;foreach&nbsp;($this-&gt;_swRequest-&gt;header&nbsp;as&nbsp;$name&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;$value)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;getHeaders()-&gt;add($name,&nbsp;$value);\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;参数信息设置\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$_GET&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&nbsp;isset($this-&gt;_swRequest-&gt;get)&nbsp;?&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swRequest-&gt;get&nbsp;:&nbsp;[];\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$_POST&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&nbsp;isset($this-&gt;_swRequest-&gt;post)&nbsp;?&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swRequest-&gt;post&nbsp;:&nbsp;[];\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$_SERVER[&#39;REQUEST_METHOD&#39;]&nbsp;=&nbsp;$this-&gt;_swRequest-&gt;server[&#39;request_method&#39;];&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;setBodyParams(null);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;setRawBody($this-&gt;_swRequest-&gt;rawContent());&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;路由设置\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;setPathInfo($this-&gt;_swRequest-&gt;server[&#39;path_info&#39;]);\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n}</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">最后提一点Yii2中的其他组件：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">errorHandler组件：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">由于 sw 程序中禁止使用exit/die 方法，所以 ErrorHandler 需要改写其中的异常退出方法。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Log 组件：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">sw提供异步写文件，这里是不是可以改进一下，写一个自己的异步写日志的组件，提高性能。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">...</p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3.结尾</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">tcp服务不在赘述，http服务相对来说更复杂写，但是明白其中解析过程（onRequest事件 -&gt; 设置yii2请求环境-&gt; 运行yii2应用）和运行原理，以及相关组件兼容写法，也就不那么难了。（写了这么多如果还是不明白，扫一扫下面的微信二维码，你就会和我一样，立马解锁更多思路）</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">附：<a href=\"https://github.com/degree66/swoole-yii2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(35, 82, 124); text-decoration: none; outline: 0px; cursor: pointer; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;\">https://github.com/degree66/swoole-yii2</a><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&quot;github原装代码&quot;</span></p>', '', 3, 563, '白衣少侠', 1, 1524362413, 1524362413);
INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (32, 'yii2教程-图表扩展（yii2-echarts）', '安装推荐通过composer安装运行以下命令phpcomposer.pharrequire--prefer-distdaixianceng/yii2-echarts&quot;*&', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 24px;\">安装</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">推荐通过composer安装</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">运行以下命令</p><pre class=\"brush:php;toolbar:false\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">php&nbsp;composer.phar&nbsp;require&nbsp;--prefer-dist&nbsp;daixianceng/yii2-echarts&nbsp;&quot;*&quot;</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">或者添加</p><pre class=\"brush:php;toolbar:false\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">&quot;daixianceng/yii2-echarts&quot;:&nbsp;&quot;*&quot;</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">到你的composer.json文件.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 24px;\">用法实例</span></strong></p><pre class=\"brush:php;toolbar:false\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">&lt;?php\r\nuse&nbsp;yii\\web\\JsExpression;\r\nuse&nbsp;daixianceng\\echarts\\ECharts;\r\n?&gt;\r\n&lt;?=&nbsp;ECharts::widget([\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;responsive&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;true,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;options&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;style&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;height:&nbsp;400px;&#39;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;pluginEvents&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;click&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;new&nbsp;JsExpression(&#39;function&nbsp;(params)&nbsp;{console.log(params)}&#39;),\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;new&nbsp;JsExpression(&#39;function&nbsp;(params)&nbsp;{console.log(&quot;ok&quot;)}&#39;)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;legendselectchanged&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;new&nbsp;JsExpression(&#39;function&nbsp;(params)&nbsp;{console.log(params.selected)}&#39;)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;pluginOptions&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;option&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;title&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;text&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;折线图堆叠&#39;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;tooltip&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;trigger&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;axis&#39;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;legend&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;data&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[&#39;邮件营销&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;联盟广告&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;视频广告&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;直接访问&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;搜索引擎&#39;]\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;grid&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;left&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;3%&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;right&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;4%&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;bottom&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;3%&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;containLabel&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;true\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;toolbox&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;feature&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;saveAsImage&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[]\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;]\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;xAxis&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;name&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;日期&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;type&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;category&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;boundaryGap&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;false,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;data&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[&#39;周一&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;周二&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;周三&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;周四&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;周五&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;周六&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;周日&#39;]\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;yAxis&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;type&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;value&#39;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;series&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;name&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;邮件营销&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;type&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;line&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;stack&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;总量&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;data&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[120,&nbsp;132,&nbsp;101,&nbsp;134,&nbsp;90,&nbsp;230,&nbsp;210]\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;name&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;联盟广告&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;type&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;line&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;stack&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;总量&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;data&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[220,&nbsp;182,&nbsp;191,&nbsp;234,&nbsp;290,&nbsp;330,&nbsp;310]\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;name&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;视频广告&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;type&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;line&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;stack&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;总量&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;data&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[150,&nbsp;232,&nbsp;201,&nbsp;154,&nbsp;190,&nbsp;330,&nbsp;410]\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;name&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;直接访问&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;type&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;line&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;stack&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;总量&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;data&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[320,&nbsp;332,&nbsp;301,&nbsp;334,&nbsp;390,&nbsp;330,&nbsp;320]\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;name&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;搜索引擎&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;type&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;line&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;stack&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;总量&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;data&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[820,&nbsp;932,&nbsp;901,&nbsp;934,&nbsp;1290,&nbsp;1330,&nbsp;1320]\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;]\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;]\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;]\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;]\r\n]);&nbsp;?&gt;</pre>', '/image/upload/20180502/1525236136470509.jpg', 5, 563, '白衣少侠', 1, 1525236200, 1525236200);
INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (33, '韩老师说', '坚持说韩老师当时就把这个王同学骂了一顿，你太不像话了，你看你的同期同学，他们薪水基本上都能够在一万以上，你为什么就不坚持下去。现在不管是摆地摊还是做开发，你都给我坚持下去。你不要今', '<p>坚持说</p><p><br/></p><p>韩老师当时就把这个王同学骂了一顿，你太不像话了，你看你的同期同学，他们薪水基本上都能够在一万以上，你为什么就不坚持下去。现在不管是摆地摊还是做开发，你都给我坚持下去。你不要今天摆地摊，遇到了城管，你明天又去当厨师。你当厨师你又觉得油烟对身体有害，又去干出租车司机，不要转来转去。人家的时间都用在了努力，而你的时间却用在了选择，当你将放弃当作一种习惯，你一辈子也不会有出息。</p><p><br/></p><p>韩老师告诉我们说，成功其实也不难，只要树立一个目标，不需要你是一个很强的人，不需要你很高智商，不需要你是千里马，你只要像老黄牛一样，每天哪怕做一点点，往目标前进一点点，你就会成功。可是成功又很难，因为在通往成功的路上，很少人能够坚持下来，在坚持的过程中，很多人都选择了“放弃”。</p><p><br/></p>', '/image/upload/20180524/1527141820641388.jpg', 1, 563, '白衣少侠', 1, 1526999681, 1526999681);

